THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, REPRESENTED IN
SENATE AND ASSEMBLY, DO ENACT AS FOLLOWS:
1 Section 1. Chapter 561 of NRS is hereby amended by adding
2 thereto a new section to read as follows:
3 1. The Director shall establish a program to assist in the
4 development of community gardens and urban farms in areas of
5 this State with high levels of food insecurity, including, without
6 limitation, areas that have been designated as food deserts.
7 2. The Director may apply for and accept any gift, donation,
8 bequest, grant or other source of money for the purpose of
9 funding the program established pursuant to this section.
